title: Modern Masquerade (1936 Musical) with Robert Young, Jessie Matthews, Sonnie Hale

sources.title: Modern Masquerade (1936 Musical) with Robert Young, Jessie Matthews, Sonnie Hale
sources.description:
Thanks to a gossip columnist, a previously unsuccessful singer becomes very popular.

Original title: It's Love Again AKA: Modern Masquerade
Directed by Victor Saville

Main cast:
Jessie Matthews - Elaine Bradford /Mrs. Smythe-Smythe
Robert Young - Peter Carlton
Sonnie Hale - Freddie Rathbone
Ernest Milton - Raymond
Robb Wilton - Boys Butler
Sara Allgood - Mrs. Hopkins
Anthony Holles - Headwaiter
Cyril Wells - Gigolo
Warren Jenkins - Woolf
David Horne - Durland
Athene Seyler - Mrs. Durland
Glennis Lorimer - Montague's typist
Robert Hale - Colonel Edgerton
Cyril Raymond - Montague
Graham Moffatt - Callboy
Olive Sloane - Francine Grenoble (uncredited)

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/Hul3_Sxg2vg
